<h1>All Posts</h1>
=begin
We iterate over each post in @posts and create a link with post.title as the text
that links to /posts/id, where the id is derived from post.id.  Instances variables
created and assigned in PostsController#index, we can use it in the posts index view.
<% @posts.each do |post| %>
  <div class="media">
    <div clas="media-body">
      <h4 class="media-heading">
        <%= link_to post.title, post %>
      </h4>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>
